{{Quote|For me, bringing in Trisha was a personal kick. One of my favorite shows growing up was ''The Courtship of Eddie's Father'' and I had remembered her from the show.|[[Robin Gurland]], Episode II Casting Director|<ref name="Casting">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/production/news20000822.html|text=Casting Update: Son of Local Talent}}</ref>}}
'''Patricia Ann Ruth Noble''' (d. [[January 23]], [[2021]])<ref name="Death" /> was an Australian singer-actress who portrayed [[Jobal Naberrie]] in both [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']], although her scenes from ''Attack of the Clones'' did not appear in the final film.

